OL,3,CDrug-related deaths increase in
OL,4,CScotland and remain highest in Europe
OL,6,FThe number of people who died in
OL,7,FScotland due to drug misuse has
OL,8,Fincreased - and remains the highest
OL,9,Fdeath rate in Europe, according to the
OL,10,Flatest figures released by the
OL,11,FNational Records of Scotland (NRS).
OL,13,FThe figures showed there were 1,172
OL,14,Fpeople who died in drug-related deaths
OL,15,Fin 2023, an increase of 121 - or 12% -
OL,16,Fon the previous year.
OL,18,FHowever, despite the rise on last
OL,19,Fyear, the new figures represent
OL,20,FScotland's second lowest number of
OL,21,Fdrug-related deaths since 2017.
